data.description: Why wait for new, when this "like new," Duval II floor plan is ready for you! If you have a need for space, this 5br, 4ba home with nearly 3800sqft, just might work for you. Upon entry, the inviting foyer w/9ft ceilings, features beautiful hardwood floors throughout the main floor living area. The formal living/office area features a custom 12ft desk w/storage, great lighting and opens to the formal dining room w/coffer ceiling & modern chandelier.  Family room w/FP overlooks the open, eat-in kitchen with large center island, quartz countertops, gas cook top, built-in oven & microwave, SS appliance, and walk-in pantry. There's one guest BR w/full bath access on the main floor. The multi use flex space off of the mudroom can be used for crafts or a reading nook.  The owners suite on 2nd floor is a dream retreat w/FP, separate sitting area, tray ceilings  and plush carpeting. Double doors open to the private bathroom w/custom tile floors,  dual vanity w/quartz counters & built in storage, separate shower, garden tub and walk-in closet. Two additional rooms have walk-in closets and share an adjoining full bath. The finished bonus room would make a great media or game room. The upstairs laundry is added convenience. Outdoor Entertaining is a breeze under the covered patio w/ceiling fan and oversized yard.  Plenty of space to  run and play or even add a pool...or 2. This home is easy to show and is sure to go quick. Call today to schedule your showing.
